{
  "stem": "14168.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I also said that in about six or eight months, I was told, that there would be a-- a group of officers, army officers, who would stage a revolt in Bolivia-- the typical Peron-type revolt.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The ambassador sort of ridiculed it, and it didn't go to Washington.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that-- the event that I had predicted occurred six or eight months later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then other things-- I had to-- we also had to do one thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to give reports on merchandise which was transshipped by German firms in Argentina which was meant for Germany and Italy, but which was addressed to Argentinian firms, who-- which in turn did the transshipment, all of this.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were fully aware of what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I also had to give reports on the economic situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because at that time, Bolivia-- America had to institute export controls, and everything that went out of the United States, exported, had to get export approval.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had to file a report with Washington on the firms who applied for the export controls, and lots of them were speculators.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- I was in charge of that program.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, in the meantime, I had the privilege of meeting some very high US officials at meetings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One was Henry Wallace, who was the vice president of the United States at the time, who came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Very enlightened man.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my-- no, my family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My in-laws were sort of self-supporting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father-in-law had gotten a job in the shipping department of a big Bolivian firm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His Spanish was poor, but he was a good worker, and so he supported himself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we lived together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had moved together.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
